<H3> <TI>   Meets State Duma Speaker Rybkin </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1803025194 Moscow INTERFAX in English 2335 GMT 17 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1803025194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow INTERFAX </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] On Thursday [17 March] Speaker of the Russian State 
Duma Ivan Rybkin met with U.S. Defense Secretary William Perry 
who is on an official visit to Moscow. 
  Chairman of the State Duma's Committee for International 
Affairs Vladimir Lukin, who attended the meeting, told Interfax 
that the meeting focused on some aspects of "pragmatic 
partnership" in the defense sphere between the two countries. 
  "It is not a tragedy that our interests in this sphere do 
not 
always coincide. These are normal relations between two great 
powers," Lukin said. 

