  [Text] Vilnius, Mar 17, BNS -- Field Marshal Richard 
Vincent, chairman of the NATO Military Committee, on Thursday 
[17 March] ended his two-day visit to Lithuania. 
  On Thursday, the NATO official met with Lithuanian President 
Algirdas Brazauskas and members of the parliament's National 
Security Committee. 
