with members of the working group that was set up to prepare a 
presentation document for Lithuania's participation in the 
Partnership for Peace program. 
  Before departure, Vincent also visited the Lithuanian field 
army brigade Gelezinis Vilkas (Iron Wolf) and met with its 
commanders. 

