<H3> <TI>   Shmarov, U.S. Envoy Discuss Upcoming Perry Visit </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  WS1703210294 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in 
Ukrainian 2000 GMT 17 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS1703210294 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Today, Deputy Prime Minister Valeriy Shmarov held a 
meeting with William Miller, ambassador extraordinary and 
plenipotentiary of the United States to Ukraine. During the 
meeting, which was held in an atmosphere of mutual understanding 
and good will, a range of pressing issues concerning the 
upcoming visit of U.S. Secretary of Defense William Perry to 
Ukraine were discussed. The parties exchanged opinions on the 
results of the recent Ukrainian-U.S. talks at the highest level. 

</TEXT>

