Ukrainian 1100 GMT 17 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS1703124094 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] President Kravchuk is resorting to the powers 
granted to him by the Ukrainian Supreme Council in regard to the 
enforcement of Ukrainian laws in the Crimea, stated Mykola 
Mykhalchenko, chief of the Presidential Service for Issues of 
Domestic Policy, commenting on the president's decree concerning 
