<F P=103> NC1903163394 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan SNARK </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Stepanakert, MARCH 19 (SNARK) -- Today there has 
been relative quietness at the Karabakh front since morning. 
SNARK was informed by the Karabakh Department of Information 
and Press at some places of the front the quietness was 
disrupted by separate skirmishes time by time. 
  Meanwhile, according to data of the same source, the 
Azerbaijani side is accumulating its troops at the eastern part 
of Karabakh front. 

