<H3> <TI>   IMF Denies Report </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2103112794 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1030 GMT 
21 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2103112794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The POSTFACTUM agency, referring to sources close to 
the leadership of the IMF, has circulated a report that talks 
between the IMF leadership and the Russian Government have 
reached an impasse. The report also says that the IMF 
leadership is examining the question of the closure of its 
mission in Moscow. The Moscow mission of the IMF told a Mayak 
correspondent that this report by the POSTFACTUM agency is 
misinformation. Talks between the IMF delegation and Russian 
representatives are continuing at present. It is expected that 
Michel Camdessus, the fund's managing director, will meet with 
Viktor Chernomyrdin, head of the Russian Government again 
tomorrow. 

</TEXT>

