<F P=100> Regional Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Soskovets Promises Financial Aid for Magnitka Combine </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PM2103114794 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 18 Mar 94 
p 3 </F>

