<H3> <TI>   Assassination Attempt Against Ingush Justice Minister </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2203115194 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1000 GMT 
22 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2203115194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radio Rossii Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] It was learned today that an attempt was made on the 
life of the Ingush Republic's justice minister at 2000 on 
Monday. His car, in which the deputy minister was also a 
passenger, was shot at from a passing motor vehicle in the 
settlement of Nizhniye Achaluki. Neither the minister nor his 
deputy were wounded but the driver was wounded and died in the 
hospital. An investigative group of the Russian Interior 
Ministry has started work at the scene of the incident. 

</TEXT>

