<F P=100> Regional Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Khabarovsk Administration `Emergency' Farm Aid Steps </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PM2203113394 Moscow PRAVDA in Russian 22 Mar 94 p 1 </F>
