<F P=102>  PM1803143394 Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI in Russian 18 Mar 94 p 
1 </F>

<F P=103> PM1803143394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report under the general headline "The Search </F>
for Accord in Russian Society Today Is Being Really Threatened 
by Political Ambitions, Mutual Distrust, and 'Double' Morals" 
and under the "In the Parliament" rubric: "Members of Factions 
See Document in Various Ways"] 
  [Excerpt] A working group of parliamentarians is being 
formed in the State Duma, which is to prepare a draft Agreement 
on Civic Peace and Accord. Alevtina Fedulova, deputy chairman 
