elaborating the draft will include representatives of all the 
parliamentary factions, who have to take upon themselves the 
task of elaborating various aspects of this document. Alevtina 
Fedulova stressed that the deputies will work in the closest 
contact with the working group, set up by Boris Yeltsin, for the 
preparation of the Agreement on Civic Peace and Accord under the 
leadership of Boris Topornin, chairman of the Russian 
presidential Public Chamber. [passage omitted] 

